  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811154/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/745af9cb8c9507baa83eed953921d314.gif\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t业界毒瘤迪士尼真的害人不浅，不光越来越发展成硬核表情包的供应商，而且还经常做些给小盆友树立错误三观的事儿。</p>\n<p>\n\t这回，英语君就来给大家盘点盘点迪士尼的那些黑时尚知识。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1. When They Made Us Believe a Fork Makes a Good Hairbrush.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1. 就是这样让我们相信叉子和梳子一样好使。</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/fbac9dc6ff48371bb8e364757b6561f3.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tWe&rsquo;ve all tried to repeat this at some point, much to our parents&rsquo; <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/disgust\" target=\"_blank\">disgust</a> and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/amusement\" target=\"_blank\">amusement</a>.我们多多少少都试过，结果要么是把粑粑麻麻给刺激到，要么是终生成为他们的笑点。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2. When They Made Dress <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Construction\" target=\"_blank\">Construction</a> Look <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Magically\" target=\"_blank\">Magically</a> Easy.2. 这时候衣服构造就简单</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">得</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">出奇</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/feac7de9fb0441e8effc8dd6f6d78000.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe fairies would have killed on Project Runway.这些仙女在《天桥风云》里估计能把评委闪瞎。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3. Same Goes with <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/alteration\" target=\"_blank\">Alterations</a>.3. 衣服改良一样如此。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/fec9c62bf51f5baec7ba7fc9afe6ffc4.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tSure, they were magical speaking mice and birds.不过毕竟，这是些神奇的会说话的老鼠和鸟。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>4. When the Shoe Always Fit Perfectly.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">4. 这时候鞋子总是正好合脚。</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/9b1c7a0c9fd9a201d37d1ded03afacaf.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThey don&rsquo;t. More lies.而这显然并没有发生。都是骗子。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>5. When They Made Us Believe We Could Give Ourselves&nbsp;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Flawless\" target=\"_blank\">Flawless</a>&nbsp;Haircuts.5. 这让我们相信我们可以自己倒腾出完美的发型。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/a19dba7687123673622b8316b8ce74f0.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThey should have put a disclaimer &mdash; &quot;Do not try this at home&quot;.就应该张贴免责声明&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;请不要在家里尝试&rdquo;。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>6. When Picking the Perfect <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Accessory\" target=\"_blank\">Accessory</a> Was Easy as Pie.6. 选最佳饰品轻而易举。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/4c8891cc090572d59176f1fb961b295b.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tIf only a gold <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/tiara\" target=\"_blank\">tiara</a> could pull every outfit together.如果真的只要戴个金王冠就能搞定所有搭配就好了。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>7. When They Made&nbsp;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Accentuating\" target=\"_blank\">Accentuating</a>&nbsp;One&rsquo;s Waist Look so Simple.7. 这让强调腰线看上去易如反掌。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/775681c868b45eab8ce9354f383bb748.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tLies, lies, lies.谎言，谎言，都是骗人的。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>8. When Lipstick and Eyeliner Went on Perfectly in one Brush <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Stroke\" target=\"_blank\">Stroke</a>.8. 唇膏和眼线都可以一笔完美成型。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/0f29bba4e0a05d6a912ef5ab970534a1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThis never happens.从来就不可能。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>9. When They Lied about What Wind Does to Hair.9. 他们还告诉你风对头发的作用是这样的。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/ba8e4b0d0a681888a81f646dd2a811b9.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>10. When Disney Had Us Believe a Hair <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Fix\" target=\"_blank\">Fix</a> Was This Obvious and Simple.10. 迪士尼让我们相信编头发简单易行。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/3199ca575dc6d7b34125f4839671b76a.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>11. When Finding the Perfect Wedding Dress Was as Easy as Kissing the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Groom\" target=\"_blank\">Groom</a>.11. 找到完美结婚礼服就和亲吻新浪一样容易。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/75d63544a26aa79d42bff9e46b3279b1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811154/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811154\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p811200/\">马云全英文演讲谈杭州和G20，高端中国英语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796619/\">这八种谈话的坏习惯，你有注意到吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p811122/\">八旬老夫妻相守62年被迫分离 这张图看哭一片</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p807011/\">时间胶囊：我想告诉年轻时的自己</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p810725/\">这个穿大裤衩啃薯条的“抠脚大汉”是卡梅伦？！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p810514/\">每天喊着老公好，你会用英语夸老公吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px